# 📊 Data Professional Survey Breakdown — Power BI Dashboard

An interactive Power BI dashboard analysing a real-world survey of 630 data professionals — covering salary, job satisfaction, programming language preferences, and career entry difficulty across global respondents.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

**Business Question:** What does the data profession actually look like in 2023 — how much do people earn, how satisfied are they, where are they from, and how hard was it to break in?

This dashboard transforms raw survey responses into a clean, single-page Power BI report using KPI cards, treemaps, gauge charts, bar charts, and a donut chart.

