## 🛠️ Tools Used

- **Power BI Desktop** — KPI cards, treemap, horizontal bar charts, gauge charts, donut chart, cross-filtering
- **Data Source:** Alex The Analyst — Data Professional Survey dataset (real survey, 630 respondents)
- **DAX** — used for average salary and average age measures

